'''''The Empire Strikes Back Weekly'' 139''' is the one hundred thirty-ninth issue of the ''[[The Empire Strikes Back Weekly]]'' series of comic reprints, published on [[October 22]], [[1980]]. A title change happens with the next issue, [[The Empire Strikes Back Monthly 140|''The Empire Strikes Back Monthly'' 140]].

==Contents==
*[[Star Wars (1977) 48|''Star Wars'' (1977) 48]] {{C|Part 4}}
*"Heroes of the galaxy: Killraven"
*"Star wars: The original story"
*"Tales of the Watcher: I Was A Prisoner Of The Martians"

